channel.title: Where can I upload a 35.6 megabyte .jar file?
channel.description:
I have a .jar file that contains the same cache as endar. The problem is though when you convert it to a cache like that you end up with a 35.6 megabyte .jar file (the .jar file is usually under 1 megabyte.) This makes it very hard to find a website that lets you upload .jar files that are that big. I need to upload it for my web-client (I already have one working I'm just updating the cache.) So I was wondering if anybody knew of an uploading website that lets you upload .jar files that big. That's all I really need to know, thanks.
If anybody would like to .jar file to try to host themselves I can email it to you if you give me your email.
